You are here: Manage Fallout

Set up how fulfillment steps are handled when they fail. For example, you can define how many times a step is retried. When an order is running, you can see in the Orchestration Plan or a list view which ones have fallen out, and retry or complete them directly.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: To configure fallout settings, from Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Fallout and SLA Settings.
title: Managing Order Fulfillment Failures
